Subject: Secunia Research: Autonomy Keyview Folio Flat File Parsing Buffer
	Overflows

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 08/04/2008

    - Autonomy Keyview Folio Flat File Parsing Buffer Overflows -

====================================================================== 
